data.description: This is a big Beautiful home with large rooms and tall ceilings on a quiet street with a farmer's field behind it and an above ground pool and a nice fire pit to relax by.  The home has had a lot of renovations done it past few years mostly on the inside.  There is a nice front porch that has been redone and a nice deck by the pool.  The kitchen has had a lot of updates as well.  Both bathrooms have been updated as well. There is a nice 1 car garage and two covered car ports as well.  It sits behind the city park as there is something to always do.  Set up a showing to see this beautiful home.
